subtests.name: Property background-size value '1px auto' computes to '1px'
Property background-size value 'auto auto' computes to 'auto'
Property background-size value 'calc(10px + 0.5em) calc(10px - 0.5em)' computes to '30px 0px'
Property background-size value 'calc(10px - 0.5em) calc(10px + 0.5em)' computes to '0px 30px'
Property background-size value 'auto 1px, 2% 3%, contain' computes to 'auto 1px'
